-> Workflow for deploying Application code 
 - Use version control
    - all codes should be in version control
    - have a READMe written for info about the application
    - app config file


 - Run the code locally
 - Make code changes
 - submit changes for review
 - run automated tests
 - merge and release
 - deploy

 Golden Rule of terraform

 -> The master branch of the live repo muste be 1:1 representation of what's actually
    deployed in production

->
